      </h2>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=267' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Zhōngwén', 'Chinese language')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">中文</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=654' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hěn', 'very')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">很</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=400' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'indicates a number greater than the number preceding it')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">多</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=8244' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fāngfǎ', 'method / way / means')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">方法</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=687' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bāokuò', 'to include')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">包括</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        In Chinese, there are many ways to express comparison, including
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '介詞 jiècí', 'preposition')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">介词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bì', 'to associate with / be near')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比</a>”
          (The preposition <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐ', 'used for comparison')" 
          onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>比</a>)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=8169' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '這個 zhège', 'this / this one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">这个</a><span class='hl'>比</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10357' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '那個 nàge', 'that')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">那个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1211' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '貴 guì', 'expensive / noble / precious')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">贵</a>。
            (This one is more expensive than that one.)
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '介詞 jiècí', 'preposition')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">介词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2021' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'and')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">跟</a>”
          (The preposition <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2022' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'with / to')" 
          onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>跟</a>.)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><span class='hl'>跟</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4789' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bà', 'father / dad')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">爸</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=781' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '一樣 yīyàng', 'same / like')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一样</a>。
            (You are the same as your father.)
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4612' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'shape / form / appearance / image')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">象</a>”
          (The verb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=11099' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'to be like')" 
          onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>象</a>)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><span class='hl'>象</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個 gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4031' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'háizǐ', 'child')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">孩子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=781' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '一樣 yīyàng', 'same / like')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一样</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4804' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '這麼 zhème', 'so much / this much / this way / like this')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">这么</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=18758' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '說話 shuō​huà', 'to speak / to say')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">说话</a>。
            (You sound like a child when you talk like that.)
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a>”
          (The verb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" 
          onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>有</a>)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><span class='hl'>有</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4789' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bà', 'father / dad')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">爸</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=953' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gāo', 'high / tall')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">高</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '嗎 ma', 'indicates a question')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>？
            (Are you as tall as your father?)
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=5964' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bùrú', 'not equal to / not as good as')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不如</a>”
          (The verb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=5964' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bùrú', 'not equal to / not as good as')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不如</a>)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><span class='hl'>不如</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4780' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '那麼 nàme', 'or so / so / so very much / about / in that case')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">那么</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1423' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǔlì', 'to strive / to try hard')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">努力</a>。
            (I am not as diligent as you.)
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '副詞 fùcí', 'adverb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">副词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=20849' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '越來越 yuè​ lái​ yuè', 'more and more')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">越来越</a>” (The adverb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20849' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '越來越 yuè​ lái​ yuè', 'more and more')" 
          onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>越来越</a>)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=5199' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lǎobǎixìng', 'ordinary people')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">老百姓</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=796' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shēnghuó', 'life')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">生活</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1857' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shuǐpíng', 'level')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">水平</a><span class='hl'>遗传</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=953' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gāo', 'high / tall')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>高</a>。
            (The living standard of ordinary people has been consistently increasing.)
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='bi'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bì', 'to associate with / be near')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a>
        Using <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐ', 'used for comparison')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>比</a> to Express Comparison
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '介詞 jiècí', 'preposition')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">介词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bì', 'to associate with / be near')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=312' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '兩 liǎng', 'two')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">两</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個人 gèrén', 'individual / personal')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个人</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huòzhě', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或者</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20428' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '性狀 xìng​zhuàng​', 'nature / character')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">性状</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=18139' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Chéngdū', 'Chengdu')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">成都</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=584' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shàng', 'above / previous')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">上</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '區別 qūbié', 'to distinguish / to discriminate')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">区别</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2769' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jùzi', 'sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=986' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīběn', 'basic / fundamental')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">基本</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6171' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'géshì', 'form / specification / format')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">格式</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        The preposition <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐ', 'used for comparison')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>比</a> can be used to express the difference in nature or degree of two people or objects.
        The basic form is:
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=399' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rén', 'person / people')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">人</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a>（<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9249' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '主語 zhǔyǔ', 'subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主语</a>） ＋ “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bì', 'to associate with / be near')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=399' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rén', 'person / people')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">人</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a>（<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '狀語 zhuàngyǔ', 'adverbial adjunct')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">状语</a>） ＋ <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        Person or thing to compare (subject) + <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐ', 'used for comparison')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>比</a> person or thing to compare (adverbial adjunct) + predicate
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=18237' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '絲綢 sīchóu', 'silk')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">丝绸</a><span class='hl'>比</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5858' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'miánhuā', 'cotton')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">棉花</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piàoliang', 'pretty / beautiful / elegant / polished')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">漂亮</a>。
          (Silk is more pretty than cotton.)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '狀語 zhuàngyǔ', 'adverbial adjunct')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">状语</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bì', 'to associate with / be near')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5858' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'miánhuā', 'cotton')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">棉花</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9379' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '修飾 xiūshì', 'to decorate / to adorn')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">修饰</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piàoliang', 'pretty / beautiful / elegant / polished')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">漂亮</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=18237' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '絲綢 sīchóu', 'silk')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">丝绸</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=5858' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'miánhuā', 'cotton')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">棉花</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piàoliang', 'pretty / beautiful / elegant / polished')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">漂亮</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1368' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chéngdù', 'degree (level or extent) / level')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">程度</a>。
            (The adverbial adjunct <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bì', 'to associate with / be near')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5858' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'miánhuā', 'cotton')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">棉花</a> modifies the predicate <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piàoliang', 'pretty / beautiful / elegant / polished')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">漂亮</a> comparing the degree of beauty of <a href='/word_detail.php?id=18237' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '絲綢 sīchóu', 'silk')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">丝绸</a> and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=5858' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'miánhuā', 'cotton')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">棉花</a>.)
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=18203' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '朝陽區 Cháoyáng Qū', 'Chaoyang District')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">朝阳区</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1258' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fángzi', 'house')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">房子</a><span class='hl'>比</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1137' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '宣武區 Xuānwǔ Qū', 'Xuanwu District')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">宣武区</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1258' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fángzi', 'house')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">房子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1211' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '貴 guì', 'expensive / noble / precious')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">贵</a>。
          (Homes in Chaoyang District are more expensive than homes in Xuanwu District.)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '介詞 jiècí', 'preposition')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">介词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bì', 'to associate with / be near')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '偏正詞組 piān zhèng cízǔ', 'an endocentric phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">偏正词组</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1137' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '宣武區 Xuānwǔ Qū', 'Xuanwu District')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">宣武区</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1258' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fángzi', 'house')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">房子</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1993' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '構成 gòuchéng', 'to constitute / to form / to compose')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">构成</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=17004' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '介詞結構 jiècí jiégòu', 'prepositional phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">介词结构</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=925' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yě', 'also')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">也</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '充當 chōngdāng', 'to serve as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">充当</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '狀語 zhuàngyǔ', 'adverbial adjunct')" 
