      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='gen'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2021' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">跟</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a>
        Using <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2022' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'with / to')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>跟</a> to Express Comparison
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '介詞 jiècí', 'preposition')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">介词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2021' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">跟</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=370' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '來 lái', 'to come')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">来</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=312' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '兩 liǎng', 'two')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">两</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個人 gèrén', 'individual / personal')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个人</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20833' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '異同 yì​tóng', 'comparison / differences and similarities')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">异同</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2021' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">跟</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1514' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '說明 shuōmíng', 'to explain')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">说明</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=312' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '兩 liǎng', 'two')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">两</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個人 gèrén', 'individual / personal')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个人</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=8537' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bù shì', 'no / is not / not')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2197' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiāngtóng', 'identical / same')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">相同</a>；<a href='/word_detail.php?id=552' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'érqiě', 'not only ... but also .... / ... as well as ... / moreover / in addition / furthermore')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">而且</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bì', 'to associate with / be near')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2730' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '具體 jùtǐ', 'concrete / definite / specific')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">具体</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '區別 qūbié', 'to distinguish / to discriminate')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">区别</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2769' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jùzi', 'sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=986' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīběn', 'basic / fundamental')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">基本</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6171' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'géshì', 'form / specification / format')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">格式</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        The preposition <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2022' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'with / to')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>跟</a> can also be used to express the diferences and similarities between two people or 
        objects.
        Use <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2022' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'with / to')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>跟</a> to explain whether two people or things are or are not the same.
        Use <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐ', 'used for comparison')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>比</a> to describe the difference more specifically.
        The basic form of such a sentence is:
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=399' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rén', 'person / people')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">人</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a>（<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9249' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '主語 zhǔyǔ', 'subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主语</a>） ＋ “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2021' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">跟</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=399' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rén', 'person / people')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">人</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a>（<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '狀語 zhuàngyǔ', 'adverbial adjunct')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">状语</a>） ＋ <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        Person or thing to compare (subject) + <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2022' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'with / to')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>跟</a> Person or thing to compare (adverbial adjunct) + predicate
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><span class='hl'>跟</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=781' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '一樣 yīyàng', 'same / like')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一样</a>。
          (I am the same as you.)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9292' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '代詞 dàicí', 'pronoun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">代词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '充當 chōngdāng', 'to serve as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">充当</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9249' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '主語 zhǔyǔ', 'subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主语</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=17004' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '介詞結構 jiècí jiégòu', 'prepositional phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">介词结构</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2021' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">跟</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '狀語 zhuàngyǔ', 'adverbial adjunct')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">状语</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '形容詞 xíngróngcí', 'adjective')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">形容词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=781' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '一樣 yīyàng', 'same / like')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一样</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a>。
            (The pronoun <a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>我</a> acts as the subject, the prepositional phrase <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2021' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">跟</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a> is the adverbial adjunct, and the adjective <a href='/word_detail.php?id=781' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '一樣 yīyàng', 'same / like')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>一样</a> is the predicate.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '這 zhè', 'this / these')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">这</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=7586' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bēi', 'cup')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">杯</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chá', 'tea')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">茶</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9122' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèidào', 'flavor')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">味道</a><span class='hl'>跟</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=754' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nà', 'that')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">那</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=426' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bèi', 'by')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">被</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><span class='hl'>差不多</span>。
          (The flavor of this cup of tea and that cup are nearly the same.)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9803' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '常見 chángjiàn', 'common')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">常见</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '形容詞 xíngróngcí', 'adjective')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">形容词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=781' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '一樣 yīyàng', 'same / like')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一样</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=10532' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chà bu duō', 'almost / nearly / more or less')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">差不多</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2197' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiāngtóng', 'identical / same')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">相同</a>”。
            (Frequently used predicate adjectives include, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=781' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '一樣 yīyàng', 'same / like')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一样</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=10532' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chà bu duō', 'almost / nearly / more or less')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">差不多</a>、and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2197' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiāngtóng', 'identical / same')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">相同</a>.)
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='xiang'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4612' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'shape / form / appearance / image')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">象</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a>
        Using <a href='/word_detail.php?id=11099' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'to be like')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>象</a> to Express Comparison
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4612' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'shape / form / appearance / image')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">象</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=312' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '兩 liǎng', 'two')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">两</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個人 gèrén', 'individual / personal')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个人</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20834' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiāng​xiàng', 'to resemble / to be similar')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">相像</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=986' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīběn', 'basic / fundamental')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">基本</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6171' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'géshì', 'form / specification / format')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">格式</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        The verb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=11099' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'to be like')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>象</a> can be used to express that two people or object resemble one another.
        The basic form is:
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=399' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rén', 'person / people')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">人</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a>（<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9249' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '主語 zhǔyǔ', 'subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主语</a>）＋ “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4612' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'shape / form / appearance / image')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">象</a>”（<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a>）　＋　<a href='/word_detail.php?id=399' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rén', 'person / people')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">人</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '事物 shìwù', 'thing / object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事物</a>（<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9260' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '賓語 bīnyǔ', 'object')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">宾语</a>）
      </p>
      <p>
        Person or thing (Subject) + <a href='/word_detail.php?id=11099' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'to be like')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>象</a> (predicate) + Person or thing (object)
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a><span class='hl'>象</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個 gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20835' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiǎo​chǒu', 'a clown')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">小丑</a>。
          (He looks like a clown.)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4612' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'shape / form / appearance / image')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">象</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=370' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '來 lái', 'to come')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">来</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1349' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '比較 bǐjiào', 'to compare / to contrast')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比较</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9249' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '主語 zhǔyǔ', 'subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主语</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9260' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '賓語 bīnyǔ', 'object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">宾语</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=20835' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiǎo​chǒu', 'a clown')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">小丑</a>“。
            (The verb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=11099' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'to be like')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>象</a> is used to compare the subject <a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>他</a> and the object of the sentence <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20835' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiǎo​chǒu', 'a clown')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>小丑</a>.)
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><span class='hl'>象</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4015' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '媽媽 māma', 'mother')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">妈妈</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4780' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '那麼 nàme', 'or so / so / so very much / about / in that case')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">那么</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4756' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '愛心 àixīn', 'compassion')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">爱心</a>。
          (You are so compassionate, just like your mother.)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4612' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'shape / form / appearance / image')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">象</a>”、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=16973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '偏正詞組 piān zhèng cízǔ', 'an endocentric phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">偏正词组</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4015' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '媽媽 māma', 'mother')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">妈妈</a>”、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9304' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '指示代詞 zhǐshì dàicí', 'demonstrative pronoun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">指示代词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4780' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '那麼 nàme', 'or so / so / so very much / about / in that case')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">那么</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1993' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '構成 gòuchéng', 'to constitute / to form / to compose')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">构成</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '狀語 zhuàngyǔ', 'adverbial adjunct')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">状语</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4612' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'shape / form / appearance / image')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">象</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4015' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '媽媽 māma', 'mother')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">妈妈</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4780' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '那麼 nàme', 'or so / so / so very much / about / in that case')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">那么</a>”；<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '形容詞 xíngróngcí', 'adjective')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">形容词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4756' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '愛心 àixīn', 'compassion')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">爱心</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '充當 chōngdāng', 'to serve as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">充当</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a>。
            (The verb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=11099' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'to be like')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>象</a>, the endocentric phrase <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4015' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '媽媽 māma', 'mother')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">妈妈</a>, and the demonstrative pronoun <a href='/word_detail.php?id=10358' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '那麼 nàme', 'like that / in that way')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>那么</a> form the adverbial adjunct <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4612' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'shape / form / appearance / image')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">象</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4015' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '媽媽 māma', 'mother')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">妈妈</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4780' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '那麼 nàme', 'or so / so / so very much / about / in that case')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">那么</a>.  The adjective <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4756' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '愛心 àixīn', 'compassion')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>爱心</a> acts as the predicate.)
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
